data.meta_description: Literary Figure. His daughter, Laura Ingalls Wilder, immortalized him and the rest of her family in the popular Little House series of books. He was born the fourth of eleven children in Cuba, New York. When he was 12, his family moved to Illinois, and then to Wisconsin. He married Caroline Lake Quiner in February...
